room_title: Escape room "The Serial Killer's Lair" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
room_description: You and your friends will be thrust into a “Jigsaw-like” serial killer lair. Here you will be watched and tormented by an unknown stalker. Experience a series of traps set by the killer. Solve his riddles and pass his tests to unlock your freedom. Otherwise, he will catch up to you in an hour.
